{
  "title": "Tangy Light Filipino Chicken Bake",
  "description": "A zesty and flavorful Filipino-inspired dish made with chicken, red chilli powder, and a hint of citrus, perfect for a solo dinner. This recipe is low in calories and rich in protein.",
  "cuisine": "Filipino",
  "diet": [
    "low-calorie",
